      由<nbsp><math|<with|math-level|0|math-display|true|<big|sum><rsub|n=1><rsup|\<infty\>>x<rsup|4*n>>><nbsp>的收敛域为<nbsp><math|<around*|(|-1,1|)>>，<equation*|<big|sum><rsub|n=1><rsup|\<infty\>><around*|(|<frac|1|2>|)><rsup|2*n+1>*x<rsup|4*n+2>> 的收敛区间为<nbsp><math|<around*|(|-<sqrt|2>,<sqrt|2>|)>>，

