      【解析】

      对 A 选项，取 <equation*|f<around*|(|x|)>=<around*|{|<tabular|<tformat|<cwith|1|-1|1|1|cell-halign|l>|<cwith|1|-1|2|2|cell-halign|l>|<table|<row|<cell|<with|math-level|0|math-display|false|x<rsup|2>+1>>|<cell|<with|math-level|0|math-display|false|x\<less\>0>>>|<row|<cell|<with|math-level|0|math-display|false|x>>|<cell|<with|math-level|0|math-display|false|x\<geq\>0>>>>>>|\<nobracket\>>>，知<nbsp><math|f<around*|(|0|)>><nbsp>不是极小值，排除。

