      <item>已知有界区域<nbsp><math|\<Omega\>><nbsp>由曲面<nbsp><math|z=<sqrt|4-x<rsup|2>-y<rsup|2>>><nbsp>与<nbsp><math|z=<sqrt|x<rsup|2>+y<rsup|2>>><nbsp>围成，函数<nbsp><math|f<around*|(|u|)>><nbsp>连续，则<nbsp><math|<big|iiint><rsub|\<Omega\>>f<around*|(|x<rsup|2>+y<rsup|2>+z<rsup|2>|)>*\<mathd\>V=>

      (A)<nbsp><math|<big|int><rsub|0><rsup|2*\<pi\>>\<mathd\>\<theta\>*<big|int><rsub|0><rsup|<sqrt|2>>f<around*|(|r<rsup|2>+z<rsup|2>|)>*r \<mathd\>z>

      (B)<nbsp><math|<big|int><rsub|0><rsup|2*\<pi\>>\<mathd\>\<theta\>*<big|int><rsub|0><rsup|<sqrt|2>>\<mathd\>r <big|int><rsub|r><rsup|<sqrt|4-r<rsup|2>>>f<around*|(|r<rsup|2>+z<rsup|2>|)>*r\<mathd\>z>

      (C)<nbsp><math|<big|int><rsub|0><rsup|2*\<pi\>>\<mathd\>\<theta\>*<big|int><rsub|0><rsup|<frac|\<pi\>|4>>sin\<nospace\>\<varphi\>\<mathd\>\<varphi\>*<big|int><rsub|0><rsup|2>f<around*|(|\<rho\><rsup|2>|)>*\<rho\><rsup|2>\<mathd\>\<rho\>>

      (D)<nbsp><math|<big|int><rsub|0><rsup|2*\<pi\>>\<mathd\>\<theta\>*<big|int><rsub|0><rsup|<frac|\<pi\>|4>>\<mathd\>\<varphi\>*<big|int><rsub|0><rsup|2>f<around*|(|\<rho\><rsup|2>|)>*\<rho\><rsup|2>*sin\<nospace\>\<varphi\>\<mathd\>\<rho\>>

      <with|marked-color|#aff|<marked|【答案】C>>

      【解析】令 <equation*|<around*|{|<tabular|<tformat|<cwith|1|-1|1|1|cell-halign|l>|<cwith|1|-1|2|2|cell-halign|l>|<table|<row|<cell|<with|math-level|0|math-display|false|x=rsin\<nospace\>\<varphi\>*cos\<nospace\>\<theta\>>>>|<row|<cell|<with|math-level|0|math-display|false|y=rsin\<nospace\>\<varphi\>*sin\<nospace\>\<theta\>>>>|<row|<cell|<with|math-level|0|math-display|false|z=rcos\<nospace\>\<varphi\>>>>>>>|\<nobracket\>>>，

      则 <equation*|<big|iiint><rsub|\<Omega\>>f<around*|(|x<rsup|2>+y<rsup|2>+z<rsup|2>|)>*\<mathd\>x\<mathd\>y\<mathd\>z=<big|int><rsub|0><rsup|2*\<pi\>>d*\<theta\>*<big|int><rsub|0><rsup|\<pi\>/4>d*\<varphi\>*<big|int><rsub|0><rsup|2>f<around*|(|r<rsup|2>|)>*r<rsup|2> sin\<nospace\>\<varphi\>*\<mathd\>r>。

      <item>单位矩阵经若干次互换两行得到的矩阵为置换矩阵，<math|A><nbsp>为<nbsp><math|n><nbsp>阶置换矩阵，<math|A<rsup|\<ast\>>><nbsp>为<nbsp><math|A><nbsp>的伴随矩阵，则（ ）

      (A)<nbsp><math|A<rsup|\<ast\>>><nbsp>为置换矩阵

